HOW TO CONTROL FRUIT BORER IN POMEGRANATE ?
KccAns: SPRAY ENDOSULFAN 35 EC @ 2 ML IN 1 LITER OF WATER AT 15 DAYS INTERVAL GIVE 4-5 SPRAYS .

QueryText: CONTROL OF EARLY BLIGHT IN TOMATO CROP ?
KccAns: SPRAY OF INDOFIL-M-45 @ 400GM IN 200 LITERS OF WATER/ACRE.
